  <Summary>Based on true movie events! Come visit Valentine Bluffs - The Little Town with the Big Bloody Heart! Someone has plans to film their new slasher flick in the town that helped define the genre - what could possibly go wrong, especially when they schedule the wrap party for February 14th? The suspect list is growing as a new killer emerges, but will a reunited TJ and Sarah be enough to stop them? Who is the mysterious Black Hearts Society and what link do they share with Harry Warden, the original killer with a pick axe to grind? True Love never dies... Be Mine this April and find out!</Summary>
